Sentencas: A strategy based on laser micro-processing was proposed to improve the solid oxide fuel cell performance by modifying electrode/electrolyte interface with a dimples array structure.
Titulo: Modification of electrode/electrolyte interface by laser micro-processing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Electrochemistry impedance spectroscopy (EIS) results showed that both ohmic and polarization resistance of single cell were decreased remarkably after interfacial modification.
Titulo: Modification of electrode/electrolyte interface by laser micro-processing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Moreover, the maximum power density of modified cell was increased by up to 58% at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Modification of electrode/electrolyte interface by laser micro-processing for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The microstructural images of electrode/electrolyte interface indicated that the structured interface extended the triple-phase boundary (TPB) length for electrochemical reaction, which led to the major improvement in the cell performance.
Titulo: Modification of electrode/electrolyte interface by laser micro-processing for solid oxide fuel cell
